{"type":"message","id":"d2a27b22","parentId":"2c45c6a1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:31:44.323Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 20:31:39 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-smarthome] DM | ou_0671c63ec5781695e9ca1ec20c78f94e [msg:om_x100b531c0c6d98b0b328b2e4b599d64]\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 20:31 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 12:31 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774355504316}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d13777c","parentId":"d2a27b22","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:31:48.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a new session startup. According to the system prompt, I need to:\n1. Read the required files (SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, TOOLS.md as per AGENTS.md)\n2. Greet the user in my configured persona (狐狸智能管家 - Fox Smart Home Butler)\n3. Keep it 1-3 sentences\n4. Ask what they want to do\n\nThe files have already been loaded in the Project Context, so I can see:\n- SOUL.md: I'm 狐狸智能管家 (Fox Smart Home Butler), concise, direct, report results honestly\n- IDENTITY.md: Name is 狐狸智能管家, emoji 🦊🏠\n- TOOLS.md: Quick reference for devices\n\nI should greet the user naturally in character as the fox butler, keeping it brief and asking what they need.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，我是狐狸智能管家 🦊🏠。刚上线，家里一切正常。\n\n你想做什么？调节空调、开关灯光，还是让扫地机器人干活？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":219,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":13223,"totalTokens":13448,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006198}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774355504324,"responseId":"msg_3de19c3e-1d23-4d4c-80a0-2ebc0a5c147e"}}
